    20 \u0432\u043E\u043B\u043D. \u0415\u0441\u043B\u0438 \u0443 \u0432\u0430\u0441
    \u0432\u043A\u043B\u044E\u0447\u0435\u043D AdBlock, \u0442\u043E \u0440\u0435\u043A\u043B\u0430\u043C\u0430
    \u043F\u043E\u043A\u0430\u0437\u044B\u0432\u0430\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F \u043D\u0435
    \u0431\u0443\u0434\u0435\u0442."
  _englishText: By clicking on this button, in the pause window and in the main menu,
    you can get 5 additional lives. Ads are also shown after every 20 waves are completed.
    If you have AdBlock enabled, then ads will not be displayed.
  _turkishText: "Bu d\xFC\u011Fmeye bast\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131zda, duraklatma
    penceresinde ve ana men\xFCde 5 ek can alabilirsiniz. Ayr\u0131ca, her 20 dalgan\u0131n
    tamamlanmas\u0131ndan sonra reklamlar g\xF6sterilir. Adblock'u etkinle\u015Ftirdiyseniz,
    reklam g\xF6sterilmeyecektir."
  _tmpText: {fileID: 2357481854789162843}
