  _englishText: After you kill all the enemies in the wave, a pop-up window will
    be shown about the completion of the wave.
  _turkishText: "Dalgadaki t\xFCm d\xFC\u015Fmanlar\u0131 \xF6ld\xFCrd\xFCkten sonra,
    dalgan\u0131n sona erdi\u011Fini g\xF6steren bir a\xE7\u0131l\u0131r pencere
    g\xF6sterilecektir."
