  _englishText: This is the button to add extra lives to your castle. You can get
    extra lives by watching an advertisement or opening a daily reward.
  _turkishText: "Bu, kalenize ekstra can eklemek i\xE7in bir d\xFC\u011Fmedir. Bir
    reklam izleyerek veya g\xFCnl\xFCk \xF6d\xFCl\xFCn\xFCz\xFC a\xE7arak ekstra
    can kazanabilirsiniz."
